-- Fitch Says Turkey May Be Raised in `Long Term' Provided Policies Continue
-- Mark Bentley
-- 2010-06-16T06:34:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/fitch-says-turkey-may-be-raised-in-long-term-provided-policies-continue.html

          
          
             Turkey’s country rating will be on
an upward trend in the “long term” should current policies
continue, Ayse Botan Berker, head of Fitch Turkey, said in an
interview with Bloomberg HT in Istanbul today.  
          
          


  


        